{"tid":2487714,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"面對黑暴維持法律與秩序！《模擬鎮暴 Riot Control Simulator》首度曝光","createTime":"2021-04-13T18:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T01:02:32.000Z","uid":112551,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"838bc8e9fa7d5bfbc325948012747a21cb5ed3cb","tid":2487714,"uid":112551,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"由波蘭研發團隊 Corpix Games 開發，以鎮暴為主題的模擬遊戲新作《模擬鎮暴（暫譯， Riot Control Simulator）》首度曝光，遊戲預定 2022 年先推出 PC 版，並於 2023 年登陸 PS4 / PS5 / Xbox One / Xbox Series X|S / NS 平台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/50/3effc1b6818cef635dc84b2eee1c34u5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F50%2F3effc1b6818cef635dc84b2eee1c34u5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=b8e9cd0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zk1wBuDVKTE&amp;t=57s&amp;ab_channel=UltimateGamesS.A.\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZk1wBuDVKTE%26t%3D57s%26ab_channel%3DUltimateGamesS.A.&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11De9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=b6c06541\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Zk1wBuDVKTE&amp;t=57s&amp;ab_channel=UltimateGamesS.A.</a><br />\n<br />\n遊戲發行商 Games Box S.A. 與 Ultimate Games S.A 表示，《模擬鎮暴》是款獨特的遊戲，讓玩家可以率領執法人員來維護城市街道安全，遊戲目標就是要面對抗議遊行的人潮，必要時採取行動，避免活動失控。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/45/b3cc26fb04c4845ae3d7f8400a1c34p5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F45%2Fb3cc26fb04c4845ae3d7f8400a1c34p5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=f6fc4989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《模擬鎮暴》將提供來自不同城市、多樣化的挑戰，在遊戲過程中玩家需要運用大量的技巧，針對特定狀況採取不同的策略，而遊戲也將結合道德選擇系統。玩家在遊戲中將可能運用各種裝備像是鎮暴車、水炮車甚至坦克等，而玩家也可以選擇如何處理人潮的方式，從友好的安撫到無情的鎮壓等，甚至還有非檯面上的方式，例如挑撥、滲透等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/41/ebce1c7c5243a9c440fac1becf1c34l5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F41%2Febce1c7c5243a9c440fac1becf1c34l5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=cdca78c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/42/195c809b39da9296a33e1cfe461c34m5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F42%2F195c809b39da9296a33e1cfe461c34m5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=48420cd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好似好好玩，踢走黑暴，你我有責！"},{"pid":"a0ad7a7ac509bf3a2eed2e47b8d3ff6c84a57805","tid":2487714,"uid":71766,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:28:51.000Z","msg":"有無64 DLC?<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94e38f023f56a27aa4f59cc0361ec786665fa949","tid":2487714,"uid":49955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:30:57.000Z","msg":"記你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"045e63377ac9b0b1b457b63dd2b455ce1fc45f69","tid":2487714,"uid":28853,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:38:30.000Z","msg":"有無得搵黑社會幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e351f7085d47367b1d32ea7d51e32856c9a09e6","tid":2487714,"uid":40350,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:42:43.000Z","msg":"想玩天安門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2e123ab072804aeac5bb2b83c3382a31f95ffc1","tid":2487714,"uid":396949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:46:20.000Z","msg":"呢個時候出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界都反警暴"},{"pid":"9952d5bc1dc37c7faae9d45b3f13cc119bf24e54","tid":2487714,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T00:51:55.000Z","msg":"想玩南京事件"},{"pid":"e06db5979de00bcc4bda5505df3906a2dc466c69","tid":